These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
House: townhouse, modern, wooden
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the wooden house is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the townhouse house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| House   | townhouse | modern | wooden   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, surfing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Sport   | surfing | basketball | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, van
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Transport       | jet-ski     | scooter | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, thriller
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | animation | mystery     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, soccer
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Sport         | lacrosse | swimming     | soccer |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
House: cottage, victorian, futuristic
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| House   | cottage       | victorian | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, pink, white
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who likes black is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Color           | black | white | pink |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
