.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports, horror
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the horse is the person watching sports movies##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | sports | time-travel  |
| Pet     | rat     | horse      | rabbit |

