There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german
1. the owner of the frog is the canadian##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the german is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Pet   | chinchilla | frog   | dog  |
| Nationality   | german    | canadian | dutch |

