The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, snowmobile
1. the fan of metal is in the middle##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | metal     | reggae   |
| Transport   | subway | roller | snowmobile |

