.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, electrician, security-guard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| Sport   | tennis | climbing     | swimming        |

