.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, orchid, lily
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the far left##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
3. the american is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Flower           | orchid | lily | tulip |
| Nationality   | turkish  | american      | colombian |

