.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, singing, sudoku
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dunhill, cain
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the cain-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | camping | singing | sudoku |
| Cigar   | aristoff | cain     | dunhill  |

