.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pepper, spinach
3 different games are played: chess, whist, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | spinach | cherry       | pepper  |
| Game   | monopoly  | whist | chess |

 